{
  "stem": "7832.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 19.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was afraid that maybe he was trying to-- I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was not allowed to go to the water to wash anything there anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we were pretty much-- did nothing and did everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you witness, personally, any atrocities, any--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only hard labor.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Only I saw my father and my brother come home, and how they were-- they had wounds and they were hurt from the stones or whatever they were working at.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were sick and tired, and all that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't witness anything until the trains came, and then I saw a lot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then when the trains came into the ghetto, and they-- they were-- they were taking people away, and everybody was running around everywhere just to gather the families together to be-- nobody had any objection of going, but they just wanted to go together with their families.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that wasn't important to the guards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They just-- whoever they found, they just pushed them on the trains to fill up the train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The doors closed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Whether the families were together or one person from the family was on a train, that didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then the train just went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and then another train came, and another came until they emptied the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then we were on our way to Tokaj to make wine, is what they said.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They told us to take all our valuables again, all our valuable possessions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But again, my grandmother and my mother, they-- they were sorting out things while we were in the ghetto to put together for us and to take with us, and-- and clothing.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
